title: Bee Leng's 8-Treasure Celestial Duck for Chinese New Year | Vanishing Home Recipes | CNA Insider
description: Forget the usual roast or stewed duck this Chinese New Year. Learn how to make Tang Bee Leng's unique version that takes surgical skills, a charcoal fire, and an optional whacky sense of humour. No wonder it's become a beloved family reunion dinner staple.
